data.enText: a large sea fish with white flesh that is used for food

tr: major food fish of Arctic and cold-temperate waters
lean white flesh of important North Atlantic food fish
the vessel that contains the seeds of a plant (not the seeds themselves)
harass with persistent criticism or carping
example: The children teased the new teacher
Don't ride me so hard over my failure
His fellow workers razzed him when he wore a jacket and tie
The immigrant was duped because he trusted everyone

tr: payable by the recipient on delivery

value.def: Cod are a type of large edible fish.

posc.def: Cod is this fish eaten as food.

example.ex: A Catalan speciality is to serve salt cod cold.
example.tran: 冷盘咸鳕鱼是加泰罗尼亚的一道特色菜。

value.def: You use cod to describe something which is not genuine and which is intended to deceive or amuse people by looking or sounding like the real thing.

example.ex: ...a cod documentary on what animals think of living in a zoo.
example.tran: 讲述动物如何看待动物园生活的搞笑伪纪录片
